---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact — RelayLaunch"
  description="Start a project with RelayLaunch. Submit a project request or ask a quick question — we'll respond within 1–2 business days."
>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ HERO -->
  <section class="section hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Get in Touch</span>
      <h1 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 52px);">
        Every engagement starts<br />with a conversation.
      </h1>
      <p class="section-sub">
        No commitment required. Tell us where you are and what you're trying to build —
        we'll figure out the right fit and move fast.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ CONTACT OPTIONS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="container contact-grid">

      <div class="contact-primary">
        <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Submit a Project Request</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
          Fill out our intake form on GitHub — we'll get back to you within 1–2 business days
          to schedule a discovery call.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Relay-Launch/.github/issues/new?template=project-request.yml"
          class="btn-primary"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          style="font-size: 15px; padding: 13px 24px;"
        >
          Submit a Project Request →
        </a>

        <div class="divider-label">or</div>

        <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: 26px; margin-bottom: 8px;">Ask a Quick Question</h2>
        <p style="color: var(--color-muted); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 24px;">
          Not ready to submit a full request? Have a specific question? Use the quick question form.
        </p>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/Relay-Launch/.github/issues/new?template=quick-question.yml"
          class="btn-secondary"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          style="font-size: 15px; padding: 13px 24px;"
        >
          Ask a Quick Question
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="contact-sidebar">
        <div class="card">
          <p class="section-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">What to Expect</p>
          <ol class="process-list">
            <li>
              <span class="step-num">1</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Submit your request</strong>
                <p>Fill out the form with whatever details you have. You don't need to have everything figured out.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="step-num">2</span>
              <div>
                <strong>We review and respond</strong>
                <p>Within 1–2 business days, you'll hear back to schedule a discovery call.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="step-num">3</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Discovery call</strong>
                <p>30–45 minutes. We learn your business, current tools, goals, and pain points.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
            <li>
              <span class="step-num">4</span>
              <div>
                <strong>Proposal + scoping</strong>
                <p>We send a clear proposal with scope, deliverables, timeline, and pricing. No surprises.</p>
              </div>
            </li>
          </ol>
        </div>

        <div class="card" style="margin-top: 16px; padding: 20px;">
          <p class="section-eyebrow" style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Direct Contact</p>
          <div class="direct-links">
            <a href="mailto:hello@relaylaunch.com" class="direct-link">
              <span class="direct-icon">✉</span> hello@relaylaunch.com
            </a>
            <a href="https://github.com/Relay-Launch" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="direct-link">
              <span class="direct-icon">⬡</span> github.com/Relay-Launch
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════ FAQ -->
  <section class="section" style="background: var(--color-surface);">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">FAQ</span>
      <h2 class="section-title" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">Common Questions</h2>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What do I need to know before reaching out?</h3>
          <p>Not much. Tell us what business you run, what's frustrating you most, and roughly what you're hoping to change. That's enough to have a productive first conversation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do you only work with businesses that need a full build?</h3>
          <p>No — the Signal audit package is specifically designed for businesses that want clarity before committing. Some clients start there and handle the build themselves.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>How long do projects take?</h3>
          <p>It depends on scope. A website build or automation setup can be turned around in a few weeks. A full operational infrastructure build is a multi-month engagement. We'll give you a realistic timeline upfront.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Do I need to keep paying after the build is done?</h3>
          <p>No. The Relay build delivers a self-running system. The Sustain retainer is for ongoing optimization, content, and growth — not keeping the lights on. Your automations keep running whether or not you're on a retainer.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>What industry do you focus on?</h3>
          <p>Any local or small business that serves clients directly — spas, wellness, trades, professional services, retail, restaurants, fitness, and more. The infrastructure problems are the same across industries.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-item">
          <h3>Can you work with our existing tools?</h3>
          <p>Yes. If you have tools that work and just need to be connected, that's exactly what Systems Integration Consulting is for. We don't force a full replacement — we start with what you have.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .hero { padding-top: 80px; }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 420px;
    gap: 56px;
    align-items: start;
  }

  .contact-primary { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }

  .divider-label {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 32px 0;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .divider-label::before,
  .divider-label::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  /* Process list */
  .process-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }

  .process-list li { display: flex; gap: 14px; align-items: flex-start; }

  .step-num {
    width: 26px;
    height: 26px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-green);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .process-list strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .process-list p { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* Direct links */
  .direct-links { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }

  .direct-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.15s;
  }

  .direct-link:hover { color: var(--color-text); text-decoration: none; }
  .direct-icon { font-style: normal; color: var(--color-green); }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
  }

  .faq-item h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .faq-item p { font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
